'''蘇菲亞學派'''是一个有争议的俄罗斯东正教派別，认为神的智慧（譯作：蘇菲亞）就是神的本质，并且神的智慧在世界上以某种方式表达为「有创造力的」智慧。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Sophia, the Wisdom of God|url=http://ivashek.com/en/texts/554-sophia-the-wisdom-of-god#Gl1_1|author=Bulgakov|first=Sergius|work=Bulgakoviana|access-date=2020-10-02|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112013450/http://ivashek.com/en/texts/554-sophia-the-wisdom-of-god#Gl1_1|dead-url=no}}</ref> 然而这个概念经常被誤解為在[[三位一體|三位一体]]中引入“第四位格”。 <ref>W. Goerdt in ''The Encyclodedia of Christianity'' (2008), [https://books.google.ch/books?id=lZUBZlth2qgC&pg=PA122 p. 122] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.ch/books?id=lZUBZlth2qgC&pg=PA122 |date=20180805052031 }}.</ref>

争议起源于[[近世|近世]]。在1890年代至1910年代。蘇菲亞學派是由[[弗拉基米爾·索洛維約夫|弗拉基米尔·索洛维约夫]]（1853–1900），帕维尔·弗洛伦斯基（1882-1937）和[[谢尔盖·布尔加科夫|谢尔盖·布尔加科夫]]（1871-1944） 提出。<ref>''Philosophy of Economy'' («Философия хозяйства» 1912) and ''Unfading Light'' («Свет Невечерний» 1917).{{Cite journal|title=A "gung-ho" approach towards Sophic Economy|url=http://www.unwe.bg/uploads/Alternatives/Bogatzky_ea_en_br_1_2017-10.pdf|last=Bogatzky|first=Nikolay|journal=Economic Alternatives|publisher=UNWE Publishing Complex|issue=1|year=2017|publication-place=Sofia|pages=160–86|issn=2367-9409|access-date=2020-10-02|archive-date=2017-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170329140513/http://www.unwe.bg/uploads/Alternatives/Bogatzky_ea_en_br_1_2017-10.pdf|dead-url=no}}.</ref>

1935年，部分蘇菲亚學說學者遭到[[莫斯科及全俄羅斯牧首|莫斯科及全俄羅斯牧首]]<ref>"The teaching of Professor and Archpriest S.N. Bulgakov – which, by its peculiar and arbitrary (Sophian) interpretation, often distorts the dogmas of the Orthodox faith, which in some of its points directly repeats false teachings already condemned by conciliar decisions of the Church…" Moscow Patriarchate (1935) Decision No. 93</ref>和其他俄罗斯东正教的譴責 。 <ref>Bishops' Council of the Russian Orthodox Church Abroad (1935) Decision of the Bishops' Council of the Russian Orthodox Church Abroad of the 17/30 October 1935 concerning the new teaching of Archpriest Sergei Bulgakov on Sophia, the Wisdom of God</ref>尽管布尔加科夫受到了上述的谴责，但Eulogius所委托的一个委员会对布尔加科夫的蘇菲亞学說进行了分析，发现他的体系雖然存在问题，但不是异端，因此也没有发表正式的谴责。<ref>{{Citation|title=George's Florovsky and the Sophiological controversy|journal=Rocor studies|date=2017-04-26|url=https://www.rocorstudies.org/2017/04/26/georges-florovsky-and-the-sophiological-controversy/#note-3056-72|accessdate=2020-10-02|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111220629/https://www.rocorstudies.org/2017/04/26/georges-florovsky-and-the-sophiological-controversy/#note-3056-72|dead-url=no}}.</ref>

[[托马斯·默顿|托马斯·默顿（Thomas Merton）]]研究了俄罗斯的蘇菲學家，并在其名为《Hagia Sophia》（1963）的诗中赞扬了蘇菲亚。 <ref>{{Cite web|title=Sophia|url=https://litpress.org/Products/5390/sophia.aspx|accessdate=2017-12-17|work=Liturgical Press}}</ref>

约翰（1993）和米汉（1996）指出俄国“蘇菲亞”的争议与西方[[婦女神學|女性主义神学]]中“上帝的性别”辩论之间的相似之处。 <ref>Elizabeth Johnson, ''She Who Is: The Mystery of God in Feminist Theological Discourse'' (1993){{Page needed|date=January 2018}}
